// For each face card (id in 11..13) in scoringHand, set enhancement to GOLD.
// In Lua: v:set_ability(G.P_CENTERS.m_gold, nil, true) — permanent for this round.
// The Gold enhancement adds $3 at end of round per card; no immediate chip/mult effect.
// Score.kt must mutate the card's enhancement before the main scoring loop.
